fields.name: attempt_start_msec
fields.description: Time when the attempt starts. CQ calculates this by searching for the last 'The CQ bit checked by...' message, which corresponds to the moment when the user has clicked on the CQ checkbox

fields.name: first_start_msec
fields.description: The time when CQ actually start processing the patch (first start message).

fields.name: last_start_msec
fields.description: The time when last start message was posted.

fields.name: first_stop_msec
fields.description: The time when first stop message was posted

fields.name: last_stop_msec
fields.description: The time when CQ stopped processing the patchset (last stop message). This is when attempt ends.

fields.name: committed
fields.description: True if the patch was committed in this attempt.

fields.name: was_throttled
fields.description: True if the request was throttled due to too many CLs being committed.

fields.name: waited_for_tree
fields.description: True if the request had to wait for an open tree.

fields.name: cq_name
fields.description: CQ name

fields.name: issue
fields.description: Issue ID. Maybe non-numeric for Gerrit issues.

fields.name: dry_run
fields.description: True if this attempt is a CQ dry run: CQ runs all jobs but won't commit a patch.

fields.name: no_tryjobs_launched
fields.description: True CQ did not launch any tryjobs due to NOTRY=true flag or because all tryjobs have finished before CQ started processing the patch

fields.name: custom_trybots
fields.description: True if custom trybots were used.

fields.name: failed
fields.description: True if the patch was rejected in this attempt.

fields.name: fail_type
fields.description: Reason why the patch was rejected.

fields.name: cq_pickup_latency_sec
fields.description: Time between start of request (SoR) and PATCH_START.

fields.name: cq_launch_latency_sec
fields.description: Time between start of request (SoR) and first VERIFIER_TRIGGER.

fields.name: verifier_pass_latency_sec
fields.description: Time between start of request (SoR) and first VERIFIER_PASS if it exists, Null if there is no VERIFIER_PASS.

fields.name: tree_check_and_throttle_latency_sec
fields.description: Time between VERIFIER_PASS and PATCH_COMMITTING.

fields.name: vcs_commit_latency_sec
fields.description: Time between first PATCH_COMMITTING and PATCH_COMMITTED. This also includes download patch from Rietv

fields.name: click_to_failure_sec
fields.description: Time between SoR and PATCH_FAILED (if it exists).

fields.name: click_to_patch_committed_sec
fields.description: Time between SoR and PATCH_COMMITTED.

fields.name: click_to_result_sec
fields.description: Time between SoR and PATCH_STOP, overall CQ run.

fields.name: contributing_bbucket_ids
fields.description: List of builds' buildbucket IDs that have contributed to an attempt.
